entry.def: If one person outranks another person, he or she has a higher position or grade within an organization than the other person.

example.ex: The most junior executive officer outranked the senior engineer officer aboard ship.
example.tran: 在舰船上，级别最低的副舰长也位列级别最高的轮机官之上。
